Coverage Strategy

TweetStream -> friend_ids -> Craft

Data Source -> HoverCraft -> Review -> Craft



Data Sources
Yelp -> Search['food truck, truck'] -> foreach yelp listing:
          -> lookup website url -> crawl website for links: twitter, fb -> HoverCraft





TweetStream -> pull -> queue all friend ids -> foreach queued twitter friend_id:
  -> pull -> lookup website url -> crawl website for links, fb, yelp -> HoverCraft




HoverCraft
Score for correctness




Review



Craft
Generate Craft for approved HoverCrafts


